           <h1>Think inside the box!</h1>
           <h3>Our Gift Cards are redeemable at most of our stores and services. Available at the Customer Service Centre in any denomination between $10 to $500*.</h3>
               <p>*No processing fees. Full details at the Customer Service Centre.</p>
               
           
            <p><u><strong>Gift Cards</strong></u><br />
<br />
Eastgate Square Gift Cards are available from our Customer Service Centre, located between Charm Diamond Centres &amp; Peoples Jewellers. Eastgate Square Gift Cards are available in any denomination between $10 to $500 and are packaged in a complimentary gift card holder. There are no processing fees or additional charges when purchasing the card! Gift Cards are redeemable at most of our stores &amp; services. Eastgate Square Gift Cards are not re-loadable or refundable.<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Method of Payment</strong></u><br />
<br />
Cash, VISA, Mastercard and Interac.<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Corporate Gift Card Orders</strong></u><br />
<br />
Looking for that perfect gift for your employees and have run out of fresh ideas? Why not pick a gift that offers a wide range of choices combined with convenience - give an Eastgate Square Gift Card. Gift Cards are an ideal way to acknowledge good relationships, to use as employee reward incentives, or to say thanks for a job well done!<br />
<br />
Eastgate Square Gift Cards are 100% value for your money and there is no service fees incurred with your purchase. Please contact any of our Customer Service Centre staff at 905-561-2444 if you require further assistances or to place your Corporate Order today!<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Cardholder Agreements</strong></u><br />
<br />
At the time of sale, the Gift Card will be accompanied by a cardholder agreement which gives you the terms and conditions governing the use of the Gift Card.<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Damaged, Lost or Stolen Gift Cards </strong></u><br />
<br />
If an Eastgate Square Gift Card is damaged, lost or stolen, the Cardholder may request a replacement card if the cardholder presents the original receipt for the purchase of the Gift Card or the damaged Gift Card in the case of a damaged Gift Card. Any replacement Gift Card will be issued and activated in the amount of the available balance of the Gift Card Account at the time when the replacement card is issued. No fee will be charged for this replacing damaged, lost or stolen gift cards.<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Account Maintenance Fees</strong></u><br />
<br />
There will be an account maintenance fee (AMF) of $2.50 per month after the 15 - month period following activation of the Gift Card. It will commence on the first day of the 16th month. The AMF will continue each month thereafter until the Gift Card account has a zero balance. The AMF will be automatically deducted from the Gift Card balance.<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Non-Participating Retailers</strong></u><br />
<br />
The Beer Store<br />
Continental Currency Exchange<br />
Dollarama<br />
Eastgate Dental Centre<br />
International News<br />
My Lucky Lotto<br />
Smokers Den<br />
<br />
<br />
<u><strong>Gift Card Account Balance</strong></u><br />
<br />
The balance of the Gift Card account is available by telephone at 1-800-755-8608 or visiting <a class="Site" href="//www.getmybalance.com">www.getmybalance.com</a>. Your account balance will also be on your receipt from participating Eastgate Square merchants, at the bottom of your receipt e.g. 10 x 60... the &quot;x&quot; represents the decimal of the amount of funds left on the card. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

